<page>
   <topic>FORM.LAST_PRESSED Function</topic>
   <description>The .LAST_PRESSED() method returns the name of the last button pressed when a form is opened as a dialog. See ((Using the FORM.VIEW__ method|Using the FORM.VIEW() method)) for details.</description>
  
   
   <syntax>.Last_Pressed()</syntax>
 
   <example><![CDATA[:form.view("Which_Report","Dialog")
last_button = :which_report.last_pressed()
:which_report.close()]]></example>

  <limitations>Desktop applications only.</limitations>
   <see>
